  "texts": [
    "As such, most systems pose little risk to patients.",
    "Fig. 2 Major areas of application for robots in healthcareOne of the best tasks for robots in this space is logistics and transportation (Table 1), where robots can be exceptionally accurate at given the right conditions.",
    "For example, mobile robots can fetch and deliver linen, pathology samples, medication, and food [58][59][60].",
    "These systems can automate the delivery of goods/supplies for pharmacies, nursing stations, kitchens, or laboratories; enabling operation with little disturbance to staff and patients.",
    "Another task that robots can do effectively is moving patients using autonomous motorised hospital beds."
  ]
}